<h3>常用样式</h3>
<p>基于主色调的按钮，可以是<code>button</code>，也可以用<code>a</code>模拟，视场景而定</p>
<div class="example">
<a class="zbj-btn" href="###">默认button</a>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary">主色button</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-success">成功button</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-info">提示button</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-danger">警示button</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-link">简化button</button>
</div>

<h3>常用尺寸</h3>
<div class="example">
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary zbj-btn-lg">大号按钮</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary">默认按钮</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary zbj-btn-sm">小号按钮</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary zbj-btn-xs">迷你按钮</button>
</div>

<h3>按钮禁用状态</h3>
<p>所有按钮添加<code>.disabled</code>样式，呈现统一的禁用状态。</p>
<div class="example">
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary zbj-btn-lg disabled">大号按钮</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-default disabled">默认按钮</button>
</div>

<h3>块级按钮</h3>
<p>块级按钮跟随父级宽度100%</p>
<div class="example">
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-primary zbj-btn-lg zbj-btn-block">大号按钮</button>
<button class="zbj-btn zbj-btn-info zbj-btn-block">中号按钮</button>
</div>